a-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615252\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pqd1665702648975.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pqd1665702648975.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pqd1665702648975.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pqd1665702648975\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Set Native Properties\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether native OCX properties can be modified in ProcScript using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__section_w894ab1b5b1_w895ab1b5_w896ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__table_d12614e1_d12615e1_d12616e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__table_d12614e1_d12615e1_d12616e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__table_d12614e1_d12615e1_d12616e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqd1665702648975__table_d12614e1_d12615e1_d12616e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">On Creation Time Only</code> (default)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqd1665702648975__table_d12614e1_d12615e1_d12616e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set native OCX properties only when the OCX control is instantiated.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqd1665702648975__table_d12614e1_d12615e1_d12616e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">On Each Property Modification</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqd1665702648975__table_d12614e1_d12615e1_d12616e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Allow native OCX properties to be set in ProcScript.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__section_dnx_ljk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1136757e124\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__table_d12086e1_d12087e1_d12088e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__section_dwx_njk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1136757e170\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__p_d106946e1_d106947e1_d106948e1\">Both the dynamic properties of the OCX container\n            widget and the native properties of the OCX control can be set in ProcScript using\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>. The properties of the OCX container widget are\n            recognized by Uniface and passed to the widget. The other properties are passed to the\n            OCX control.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__p_d106949e1_d106950e1_d106951e1\">During development, the static set of native\n            attributes of the OCX control are stored in the form component. This set is sent to the\n            OCX control after the control instance is created (and after each property modification,\n            if this property is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">On Each Property Modification</code>).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__p_d106952e1_d106953e1_d106954e1\">However, if this property is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">On\n               Creation Time Only</code>, you can use ProcScript to set the  autostart property as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__pre_vhq_4jk_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(\"MY_OCX_FIELD.MY_ENTITY\") = \"autostart=true\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__section_vq5_pjk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1136757e199\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__p_d108977e1_d108978e1_d108979e1\">This is a static property. It cannot be set in\n            ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqd1665702648975__section_mrb_rjk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1136757e208\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vvo1665702647716.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vvo1665702647716.html\" title=\"The uOcxContainer widget embeds a Microsoft OCX control into a form component, and maps OCX properties and OCX events to fields and triggers. You can use ProcScript to activate OCX methods and let the OCX control activate widget triggers to respond to OCX events.\">uOcxContainer (OcxContainer)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615252\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615252\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Set Native Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set Native Properties Determines whether native OCX properties can be modified in ProcScript using $fieldproperties . Value Description On Creation Time Only (default) Set native OCX properties only when the OCX control is instantiated. On Each Property Modification Allow native OCX properties to be set in ProcScript. Usage Dynamic? No Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description Both the dynamic properties of the OCX container widget and the native properties of the OCX control can be set in ProcScript using $fieldproperties . The properties of the OCX container widget are recognized by Uniface and passed to the widget. The other properties are passed to the OCX control. During development, the static set of native attributes of the OCX control are stored in the form component. This set is sent to the OCX control after the control instance is created (and after each property modification, if this property is set to On Each Property Modification ). However, if this property is set to On Creation Time Only , you can use ProcScript to set the autostart property as follows: $fieldproperties(\"MY_OCX_FIELD.MY_ENTITY\") = \"autostart=true\" Copy Using in ProcScript This is a static property. It cannot be set in ProcScript. Applies To uOcxContainer (OcxContainer) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}